Add hospital name

Source: R/legg_til_sykehusnavn.R
legg_til_sykehusnavn.Rd

Add hospital name as text string based on value of centreid. New variable is called sykehusnavn. sykehusnavn will overwrite exising variable of same name.

legg_til_sykehusnavn(df, short = TRUE)

Arguments

df

data.frame with AblaNor data. Must contain centreid.

short

boolean. Short = TRUE gives short names, short = FALSE gives complete names.

Value

Returns df with new one new column.

Examples

df <- data.frame(centreid = c(102966, 104284, 4214492, 700328, 4219765))
ablanor::legg_til_sykehusnavn(df = df, short = TRUE)
#>   centreid sykehusnavn
#> 1   102966         HUS
#> 2   104284    St.Olavs
#> 3  4214492        <NA>
#> 4   700328         OUS
#> 5  4219765         UNN
